    {
      "primary": {
        "text": [
          {
            "type": "heading2",
            "text": "the long version",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "I'm a \"full stack\" engineer by trade. You can check out my\u00a0resume\u00a0for more about that.",
            "spans": [
              {
                "start": 59,
                "end": 65,
                "type": "hyperlink",
                "data": {
                  "id": "X-EtfREAACAA8Nfy",
                  "type": "resume",
                  "tags": [],
                  "lang": "en-us",
                  "slug": "resume",
                  "first_publication_date": "2020-12-21T23:28:20+0000",
                  "last_publication_date": "2021-10-02T10:41:14+0000",
                  "link_type": "Document",
                  "isBroken": false
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "This site serves as a place for people to find out more about me, and a place for\u00a0me to write down my thoughts. Most of those thoughts will be about programming for now, so I'll keep this particular page focused on everything else.",
            "spans": [
              {
                "start": 82,
                "end": 110,
                "type": "hyperlink",
                "data": {
                  "id": "X99n4xEAACMA6OTu",
                  "type": "blog",
                  "tags": [],
                  "lang": "en-us",
                  "slug": "blog",
                  "first_publication_date": "2020-12-20T15:04:06+0000",
                  "last_publication_date": "2021-11-11T03:29:13+0000",
                  "link_type": "Document",
                  "isBroken": false
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "I'm a happily married man to my wife Jamie. We have a beautiful baby boy named Jordi and an adorable dog named Emmy.",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "I was born and raised here in Philly, though my mom's family is from Barcelona. Many moons ago I was fluent in Spanish. I do my best to maintain my skills in that language as well. I prefer travelling to Spanish speaking countries not only because I love the culture, but also because I love the practice. That's right, we're talkin' 'bout practice.",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Speaking of practice, I'm a big F.C. Barcelona fan, and an even bigger fan of the Philadelphia 76ers. I follow all Philly sports closely, but I'd say the passion level goes Sixers, Eagles, Flyers, Phillies, in that order. #trusttheprocess",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "I also enjoy playing tennis, hiking, biking, running, skiing, and snowboarding, amongst other things. I'm not much of a cook, but like most I'm dangerous with a handful of recipes. On the music front, my bag is mostly blues and rock but I've got a pretty eclectic taste.",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Oh...and my top 3 movies of all time are Forrest Gump, The Shawshank Redemption, and The Big Lebowski.",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "That's all for now. If you are interested in connecting for any reason, please don't hesitate to\u00a0reach out!",
            "spans": [
              {
                "start": 97,
                "end": 106,
                "type": "hyperlink",
                "data": {
